<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <link rel="icon" href="/icon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

        <title>Ramon Hernandez</title>
        <meta name="description" content="Ramon Hernandez - Computer Engineer and Web Developer. Passionate about clean code, Go, and web technologies.">
        <meta name="keywords" content="Ramon Hernandez, Puerto Vallarta, Web Developer, Computer Engineer, Go Developer, JavaScript, Portfolio, Tafer Resorts, Universidad de Guadalajara">
        <meta name="author" content="Ramon Hernandez">
        <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">

        <meta property="og:title" content="Ramon Hernandez - Computer Engineer Portfolio">
        <meta property="og:description" content="Computer Engineer focused on reliable software, useful web systems, and modern web technologies.">
        <meta property="og:url" content="https://monkig.dev">
        <meta property="og:type" content="website">
        <meta property="og:site_name" content="Ramon Hernandez Portfolio">
        <meta property="og:image" content="https://monkig.dev/icon-og.png">
        <meta property="og:image:type" content="image/png">
        <meta property="og:image:width" content="512">
        <meta property="og:image:height" content="512">

        <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
        <meta name="twitter:title" content="Ramon Hernandez - Computer Engineer Portfolio">
        <meta name="twitter:description" content="Computer Engineer focused on reliable software, useful web systems, and modern web technologies.">
        <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://monkig.dev/icon-og.png">
    </head>

<body>
    <main class="shell">
        <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="intro-title">
            <div class="hero-copy">
                <p class="eyebrow">Computer Engineer - Puerto Vallarta</p>
                <h1 id="intro-title">Ramon Hernandez</h1>
                <p class="lede">
                    Computer Engineer by <a href="https://udg.mx/" target="_blank">Universidad de Guadalajara</a>,
                    focused on building reliable software, useful web systems, and practical tools with clean code
                    and a constant curiosity for how things work.
                </p>
                <div class="hero-actions" aria-label="Primary links">
                    <a class="button primary" rel="me" href="https://github.com/monkig" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
                    <a class="button" rel="me" href="https://linkedin.com/in/ramonha" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section-grid" aria-label="Portfolio sections">
            <section class="panel experience" aria-labelledby="experience-title">
                <div class="section-heading">
                    <span>01</span>
                    <h2 id="experience-title">Experience</h2>
                </div>
                <ol class="timeline">
                    <li>
                        <time>March 2025 - Present</time>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Web Developer</strong>
                            <a href="https://www.taferresorts.com/" target="_blank">Tafer Resorts</a>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <time>March 2024 - August 2024</time>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Web Developer - Social Service Intern</strong>
                            <a href="https://www.cuc.udg.mx/" target="_blank">Centro Universitario de la Costa</a>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </section>

            <section class="panel languages" aria-labelledby="languages-title">
                <div class="section-heading">
                    <span>02</span>
                    <h2 id="languages-title">Languages</h2>
                </div>
                <p>
                    I have worked with and experimented across a wide range of languages, so adapting to a new stack
                    is usually straightforward: understand the idioms, learn the tooling, and build with intention.
                </p>
                <ul class="language-list" aria-label="Languages and tools">
                    <li>Go</li>
                    <li>JavaScript</li>
                    <li>TypeScript</li>
                    <li>PHP</li>
                    <li>Python</li>
                    <li>SQL</li>
                    <li>HTML</li>
                    <li>CSS</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="panel projects" aria-labelledby="projects-title">
                <div class="section-heading project-heading">
                    <span>03</span>
                    <h2 id="projects-title">Projects</h2>
                </div>
                <ul id="github-projects" class="project-list" aria-live="polite">
                    <li class="muted">Loading projects...</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </section>

    </main>

    <script src="/main.js" is:inline></script>
</body>
</html>

<style>
    :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --ink: #151515;
        --muted: #63615b;
        --line: #d8d1c3;
        --paper: #f7f4ee;
        --accent: #0d6b5f;
        --accent-strong: #094f47;
        --warm: #ad5d2b;
        --soft: rgba(13, 107, 95, 0.08);
        font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    }

    * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--ink);
        background: var(--paper);
    }

    a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration-color: rgba(13, 107, 95, 0.35);
        text-decoration-thickness: 0.12em;
        text-underline-offset: 0.2em;
    }

    a:hover {
        color: var(--accent-strong);
    }

    .shell {
        width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 48px 0;
    }

    .hero {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: clamp(360px, 56vh, 520px);
        padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 64px) 0 40px;
    }

    .hero-copy {
        display: grid;
        width: 100%;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.15fr) minmax(280px, 0.85fr);
        column-gap: clamp(32px, 7vw, 88px);
        align-items: end;
    }

    .hero-copy::before {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        width: 72px;
        height: 4px;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        background: var(--accent);
        content: "";
    }

    .eyebrow {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        margin: 0 0 18px;
        color: var(--accent-strong);
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    h1,
    h2,
    p {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    h1 {
        grid-column: 1;
        max-width: 840px;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        font-size: clamp(3.6rem, 10vw, 7.5rem);
        line-height: 0.9;
        letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .lede {
        grid-column: 2;
        max-width: 720px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        color: #333;
        font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.4vw, 1.65rem);
        line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .hero-actions,
    .link-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 18px;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
    }

    .hero-actions {
        grid-column: 2;
    }

    .button,
    .link-list a {
        display: inline-flex;
        min-height: 36px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 0 0 5px;
        background: transparent;
        font-weight: 800;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-decoration-color: currentColor;
        text-decoration-thickness: 0.12em;
        text-underline-offset: 0.35em;
    }

    .button.primary,
    .link-list a:hover {
        color: var(--accent-strong);
    }

    .section-grid {
        --section-gap: clamp(24px, 5vw, 56px);
        position: relative;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
        gap: var(--section-gap);
        padding-top: 38px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .section-grid::before {
        position: absolute;
        top: 38px;
        bottom: 0;
        left: calc(((100% - (5 * var(--section-gap))) / 6 * 4) + (3.5 * var(--section-gap)));
        width: 1px;
        background: var(--line);
        content: "";
    }

    .experience,
    .projects {
        grid-column: span 4;
    }

    .languages {
        grid-column: span 2;
    }

    .section-heading {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .section-heading span {
        color: var(--warm);
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .project-heading {
        justify-content: space-between;
        text-align: right;
    }

    .projects {
        position: relative;
    }

    h2 {
        margin-bottom: 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.6vw, 2rem);
        letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .timeline,
    .project-list,
    .language-list {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
    }

    .timeline {
        display: grid;
        gap: 24px;
    }

    .timeline li {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(160px, 0.44fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: 18px;
        padding-bottom: 24px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .timeline li:last-child {
        padding-bottom: 0;
        border-bottom: 0;
    }

    time,
    .muted {
        color: var(--muted);
    }

    .timeline strong,
    .project-list a {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.08rem;
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .timeline a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .languages p {
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .language-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .language-list li {
        padding: 7px 10px;
        background: var(--soft);
        color: var(--accent-strong);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        font-weight: 800;
    }

    .project-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
    }

    .project-list li {
        padding: 0 0 14px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .project-list li:last-child {
        padding-bottom: 0;
        border-bottom: 0;
    }

    .project-list a {
        color: var(--ink);
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
        .shell {
            width: min(100% - 24px, 680px);
            padding: 22px 0;
        }

        .section-grid,
        .timeline li {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: auto;
            padding: 20px 0 16px;
        }

        .hero-copy {
            display: flex;
            min-height: auto;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .experience,
        .projects,
        .languages {
            grid-column: span 1;
        }

        .section-grid {
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .section-grid::before {
            display: none;
        }
    }
</style>
